  <brief_title>RCT of Continuous Versus Intermittent Infusion of Vancomycin in Neonates</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomised Controlled Trial (RCT) of Continuous and Intermittent Infusion of Vancomycin in Neonates</official_title>
